anen</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500\">Plane perfekte Urlaubstage mit Stränden, Märkten und Restaurants.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/80 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-4xl text-teal-600\">♡</div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-base font-extrabold\">Favoriten</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500\">Speichere deine Lieblingsorte für später.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/80 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-4xl text-teal-600\">★</div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-base font-extrabold\">Geheimtipps</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500\">Entdecke Orte abseits der typischen Touristenpfade.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/80 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-4xl text-teal-600\">🎒</div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-base font-extrabold\">Packliste</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500\">Nie wieder etwas Wichtiges für Thailand vergessen.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/80 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-4xl text-teal-600\">🤖</div><h3 class=\"mt-5 text-base font-extrabold\">KI-Assistent</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500\">Erhalte Antworten und Tipps rund um Khao Lak.</p></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-8 py-0 md:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-b