nter justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-sm text-white\">✓</span>Offline-Nutzung später geplant</div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 text-center md:grid-cols-3\"><div><div class=\"text-5xl font-black text-teal-500\">800+</div><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600\">Verkaufte Khao-Lak-Guides.</p></div><div><div class=\"text-5xl font-black text-teal-500\">100+</div><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600\">Orte, Strände, Restaurants und Geheimtipps.</p></div><div><div class=\"text-5xl font-black text-teal-500\">2026</div><p class=\"mt-3 text-slate-600\">Start der Khao Lak Insider App.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"waitlist\" class=\"px-8 py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-600 px-8 py-16 text-center text-white shadow-2xl shadow-teal-100\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full bg-white/20 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold backdrop-blur\">Khao Lak Insider App</div><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-black leading-tight md:text-5xl\">Verpasse den Start nicht.</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-white/90\">Trage dich unverbindlich in die Warteliste ein und erfahre als Erster, wenn die Khao Lak Insider App startet.</p><form class=\"mx-auto mt-9 flex max-w-xl flex-col gap-4 rounded-3xl bg-white p-2 shadow-xl sm:flex-row sm:rounded-full\"><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Deine E-Mail-Adresse\" class=\"h-12 flex-1 rounded-full px-5 text-slate-900 outline-none\" value=\"\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-950 px-7 font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60\">Zur Warteliste</button></form><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-white/75\">Kein Spam. Nur Informationen zum App-Start.</p></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]\"><d